    dc:description "Lower end of normal range or reference range for standardized results (e.g., OESTRESC, OESTRESN) represented in standardized units (OESTRESU)." ;
    dc:identifier "OESTNRLO" .

<http://id.gsk.com/dataset/cdisc/sdtm-ig/v3-4/OE/OESTRESC> a sdtmig:Variable ;
