        <http://id.gsk.com/dataset/cdisc/sdtm-ig/v3-4/PE/PETEST>,
        <http://id.gsk.com/dataset/cdisc/sdtm-ig/v3-4/PE/PETESTCD>,
        <http://id.gsk.com/dataset/cdisc/sdtm-ig/v3-4/PE/STUDYID>,
